Awesome, missed it last night. 

Howzat! Kerry Packer's War is an Australian drama-miniseries set in the 1970's that commenced airing on the Nine Network in August 2012. It premiered on Sunday August 19, 2012 .The story line is a dramatisation of the events that lead up to and the establishment of World Series Cricket in the period 1977 to 1979.
